---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import SpotlightImage from '../../components/SpotlightImage.astro';
---
<MainLayout 
  title="Local SEO Services Orange County CA | OCWebPros" 
  description="Local SEO for Orange County businesses. Google Business Profile optimization, photo uploads, post scheduling, citation management, and content strategy. Plans from $500/mo."
  bodyClass="page-services page-local-seo"
  pageCSS="/css/pages/services.css">

  <header class="relative pt-32 sm:pt-32 md:pt-40 pb-12 sm:pb-16 px-4 sm:px-6 text-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[90vw] max-w-[800px] h-[400px] sm:h-[500px] md:h-[600px] glow-bg pointer-events-none opacity-40"></div>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto relative">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 text-xs font-medium text-orange-400 mb-6">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-500 animate-pulse"></span>
        Local SEO
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">
        Local SEO in <span class="text-gradient-orange">Orange County</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Make it easy for nearby customers to find and contact you across Google Search and Maps - with ongoing optimization, not one-time fixes.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mt-8">
        <a href="/contact/" class="px-8 py-3.5 bg-orange-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-orange-600 transition-colors btn-glow text-sm md:text-base">
          Get a Free Audit
        </a>
        <a href="/pricing/" class="px-8 py-3.5 bg-slate-100 text-slate-900 font-semibold rounded-full border border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors text-sm md:text-base">
          View Pricing
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="pb-16 sm:pb-24 px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8">
    <!-- Spotlight -->
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto pt-8 md:pt-12 pb-16 md:pb-24 px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-12">
        <SpotlightImage
          class="order-1"
          aos="fade-left"
          src="/images/unsplash/services-local-seo.jpg"
          alt="Local business search results on a phone map"
        />
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 backdrop-blur-[12px] bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 order-2" data-aos="fade-right">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">Get Found by Local Customers</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">When someone in Orange County searches for your service, you should show up - in organic results, on Google Maps, and across the platforms that influence local rankings.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-500 flex-shrink-0"></span><span>Google Business Profile setup, optimization, and regular posts</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-500 flex-shrink-0"></span><span>On-page SEO: titles, meta, headings, and internal links</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-500 flex-shrink-0"></span><span>Regular photos, posts, and performance reports</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-500 flex-shrink-0"></span><span>Citation consistency across Yelp, Bing, and local directories</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing Tiers -->
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto pt-4 md:pt-8 pb-12 md:pb-16 px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="relative text-center mb-8" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-72 h-48 md:w-96 md:h-56 bg-gradient-to-tr from-orange-500/15 to-sky-500/15 blur-3xl rounded-full pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 text-xs font-medium text-orange-400 mb-4">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-500 animate-pulse"></span>
            Local SEO Pricing
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">Choose your plan</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm md:text-base">Monthly packages to fit your business needs</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Tier 1: The Foundation -->
        <div class="local-seo-pricing-card backdrop-blur-[12px] border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 overflow-hidden relative flex flex-col transition-all duration-300 ease-out" style="background: #ffffff;">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500/10 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tl from-orange-500/5 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          <div class="relative flex flex-col flex-1">
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">The Foundation</h3>
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">
                <span class="text-lg align-top">$</span>500
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">per month</p>
              <p class="text-orange-400 text-xs font-medium mt-2">Who is this for? Visibility Upkeep</p>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mt-2">For established businesses that need to keep their digital doors open and technical health green.</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 flex-1">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-slate-700">Google Map Protection: Weekly posts &amp; spam fighting.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-slate-700">Search Health Monitor: Monthly crawl errors, index issues, and broken internal link fixes.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-slate-700">Review Management: Monitor Google &amp; Yelp, alert you to every new review, and flag suspicious or policy-violating ones.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-slate-700">Citation Upkeep: Keeping your address consistent on Yelp/Bing.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/pricing/" class="block w-full px-6 py-3 bg-slate-100 text-slate-900 font-semibold rounded-full text-center border border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors text-sm mt-auto">
              Get Started
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tier 2: The Growth Engine (Featured) -->
        <div class="local-seo-pricing-card backdrop-blur-[12px] border-2 border-orange-500/50 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 overflow-hidden relative flex flex-col transition-all duration-300 ease-out" style="background: #ffffff;">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500/10 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tl from-orange-500/5 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-orange-700 text-white text-xs font-semibold rounded-full">Recommended</span>
          </div>
          <div class="relative flex flex-col flex-1">
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">The Growth Engine</h3>
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">
                <span class="text-lg align-top">$</span>1,250
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">per month</p>
              <p class="text-orange-400 text-xs font-medium mt-2">Who is this for? Expansion Mode</p>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mt-2">For businesses ready to expand their service area and capture high-intent leads from competitors.</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 flex-1">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/20 transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-emerald-500/10 hover:border-emerald-500/30">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-400">Everything in Foundation, PLUS:</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-slate-700">2 Strategic Articles/Mo: We write content that answers customer questions.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-slate-700">Competitor Gap Analysis: Find and capture keyword opportunities your competitors are ranking for.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-slate-700">Local Link Building: Monthly outreach to relevant local sites, directories, and community resources.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-slate-700">On-Page SEO Optimization: Keyword-focused updates to titles, headings, internal links, and page copy.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-slate-700">Live Dashboard: 24/7 view of your keyword rankings.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/pricing/" class="block w-full px-6 py-3 bg-orange-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-full text-center hover:bg-orange-600 transition-colors btn-glow text-sm mt-auto">
              Get Started
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tier 3: Market Dominance -->
        <div class="local-seo-pricing-card backdrop-blur-[12px] border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 overflow-hidden relative flex flex-col transition-all duration-300 ease-out" style="background: #ffffff;">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500/10 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tl from-orange-500/5 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          <div class="relative flex flex-col flex-1">
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Market Dominance</h3>
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">
                <span class="text-lg align-top">$</span>3,000
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">per month</p>
              <p class="text-orange-400 text-xs font-medium mt-2">Who is this for? Aggressive Growth</p>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mt-2">For franchises or aggressive brands that want to be the undisputed #1 choice in the region.</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 flex-1">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/20 transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-emerald-500/10 hover:border-emerald-500/30">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-400">Everything in Growth, PLUS:</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-slate-700">Double Content Velocity: 4 High-impact articles per month.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-slate-700">Conversion Rate Optimization (CRO): Ongoing analysis to identify and fix issues preventing visitor conversions.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-slate-700">Local Media Outreach: Online press releases with Orange County local angles, published on your site and distributed through major PR channels.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-slate-700">Monthly Conversion Audit: We analyze your site and suggest improvements to increase leads.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/pricing/" class="block w-full px-6 py-3 bg-slate-100 text-slate-900 font-semibold rounded-full text-center border border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors text-sm mt-auto">
              Get Started
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Grid -->
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto pt-2 md:pt-4 pb-16 md:pb-24 px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">What We Optimize</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm md:text-base">Local search visibility depends on more than keywords - here&apos;s what we cover.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="0">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">On-Page Foundations</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Title tags, meta descriptions, headings, internal links, and clear service/location pages.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Google Business Profile</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Setup, categories, services, photos, and posting cadence to support Maps visibility.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V9.414a1 1 0 00-.293-.707l-5.414-5.414A1 1 0 0012.586 3H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Content &amp; Schema</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">City/service content, basic schema where it helps, and sensible internal linking.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Technical Hygiene</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Core Web Vitals, indexation, sitemaps, redirects, and clean site structure.</p>
        </div>
